"reviewcomment":"I went both to the Paris and Barcelona locations of Bubbolitas within a week -- hopefully my loyal-customer prize is in the mail!<br><br>Why did I go to such an effort of tracking down this place after finding it first in Barcelona? Because they do frozen coconut bubble tea with both tapioca pearls and coconut jelly (of which they have three flavors) and it is AMAZING. Perfectly blended, creamy, a good balance of tea and milk flavors. <br><br>There are tons of options for teas, so take your time and choose carefully. They also had empanadas which were pretty good, though not on the level of the bubble tea. We went back twice, it was that good.",
